additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. First Aid - If medical advice is needed, contact a doctor or Poisons Information Centre (AUS 13 11 26) and have product pack at hand. If ingested, rinse mouth out with water. Do not induce vomiting.

description: Samba 100% Natural Firelighters are non toxic, clean to handle and ideal for all fire lighting applications. These high performing firelighters are perfect for firing up your charcoal BBQ, or indoor fireplace quickly and easily.
name: Natural Firelighters
